	name = "'The Shitbucket' Plaque";
	desc = "A stamped steel sign reading 'This vessel, nicknamed the Shitbucket, was assembled by Technician Akesi-Bhzl of the SV Canterbury on 01/03/507 FS after a blunder by the command staff of the SV Canterbury left them stranded on a jungle-world, with no supplies available bar the wreckage of a Condor-class. This vessel would subsequently take off from that world, having been improvised by Akesi, and would rendezvous with the Canterbury at Thousand Eyes, a Cybersun outpost. It was subsequently transported back to Requiem and placed in storage here. The flight control system has been disabled for safety reasons, though it is still powered and may be reactivated if the need arises.'"
